Sentencas: The electrochemical performances were investigated for proton-conducting solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs) with the perovskite-type oxide cathodes.
Titulo: Fabrication of BaCe0.8Y0.2O3 dense film on perovskite-type oxide electrode substrates

Sentencas: As for proton-conducting SOFC using BaCe0.8Y0.2O3 (BCYO) and SrCe0.95Yb0.05O3 (SCYO) electrolytes, La0.7Sr0.3O3 (LSFO) cathode showed the best electrochemical performance among the perovskite-type oxides tested in the present study.
Titulo: Fabrication of BaCe0.8Y0.2O3 dense film on perovskite-type oxide electrode substrates

Sentencas: The spin-coating technique was applied to fabricate BCYO thin film on the LSFO substrate.
Titulo: Fabrication of BaCe0.8Y0.2O3 dense film on perovskite-type oxide electrode substrates

Sentencas: With this technique, dense and crack-free BCYO thin film could be fabricated on LSFO electrode substrate.
Titulo: Fabrication of BaCe0.8Y0.2O3 dense film on perovskite-type oxide electrode substrates

Sentencas: the electrical conductivity of BCYO thin film fabricated on LSFO electrode substrate was lower than that of the bulk BCYO specimen.
